title: Advicent.FactFinderService
description: An API for accessing the Narrator Fact Finder.

actions.title: AccountTypes_GetByCountry
actions.description:
Description: This operation retrieves all Account Types for the specified country.
Purpose: Provides access to the Account Types including id and type description.

country.description: The country used to filter Account Types

actions.title: AccountTypes_GetById
actions.description:
Description: This operation retrieves all Account Types for the specified id.
Purpose: Provides access to the Account Types including id and type description.

id.description: The ID of Account Type used to retreive the Account Type information

actions.title: Accounts_GetAccountsByFactFinderIdByFactfinderidExternalsourceid
actions.description:
Description: This operation retrieves all Accounts for the specified Fact Finder ID and/or external source ID.
Purpose: Provides access to the Account information including description and market value.

factFinderId.description: The ID of the Fact Finder used to retrieve Accounts

externalSourceId.description: The external ID used to filter Accounts

actions.title: Accounts_PostByModel
actions.description:
Description: The operation creates an Account.
Purpose: Allows for creation of Accounts on a Fact Finder.

actions.title: Accounts_GetAccountHoldingByAccountidId
actions.description:
Description: This operation retrieves a single Account Holding for the specified Account Holding ID and Account ID.

accountId.description: The ID of the Account used to retreive the Account Holding data

id.description: The ID of the Account Holding used to retreive the Account Holding data

actions.title: Accounts_DeleteAccountById
actions.description:
Description: The operation removes an Account tied to a Fact Finder.
Purpose: Allows for removal of an Account from a Fact Finder.

id.description: The Account ID used to identify which Account to remove

actions.title: Accounts_GetById
actions.description:
Description: This operation retrieves a single Account for the specified Account ID.
Purpose: Provides access to the Account information including description and market value.

id.description: The ID of the Account used to retreive the Account data

actions.title: Accounts_PutByIdModel
actions.description:
Description: The operation updates an Account.
Purpose: Allows for complete replacement of an Account on a Fact Finder.

id.description: The existing Account ID used to identify which Account to update

actions.title: Clients_PostByModel
actions.description:
Description: This operation submits the Fact Finder data to an external system.
